window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p><b>Contains the complete Wardens of Issalia series, an action-packed fantasy adventure saga filled with deception, destruction, and some serious fire-powered weapons. </b></p> <p>Everson is mentally gifted, and yet, he feels broken. Cursed with non-functional legs, he dreams of nothing more than being useful. His sister, Quinn, is brave, relentless, and will do anything to protect him, so when Everson is sent to a school of magic and invention, Quinn joins a military academy to remain near him.</p> <p>Danger lurks within the fabled institutions. Quinn becomes embroiled in a struggle she doesn't understand, one with dire consequences as her training shifts from difficult to deadly. Her relentless determination might help her survive. If she only knew whom she could trust. Within the other school, Everson studies a dangerous magic known as Chaos. Unable to wield this magic, he melds it with science, dreaming up inventions to reshape the future. His greatest discovery might change the world...or it could destroy everything.</p> <p>Join Everson, Quinn, and magic-wielding friends as they attempt to harness a magical power source to act as the Kingdom of Issalia's shield against tyranny.</p>"; 
